      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GRAMERCY GARRY (3) dropped out early but hit the line hard, charging into second and beaten 6 lengths win (29.94) at this track in Grade 5. Goes very well from this box. The form out of his last race has been franked. Likely to feature again. SKEDADDLE ARLO (7) brought up his 22nd career win last start at this track (36.12). Has a strong winning record here at this journey. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Can make it back-to-back wins. SIN CITY BANDIT (1) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (36.93) at this track behind SKEDADDLE ARLO in a Grade 4/5. Turned chasing the leaders but kept coming. Expected to feature. BLACK TIARA (4) missed the placings here last start but is well-placed to turn the form around.",
